{
  "stem": "16345.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I wanted food, I asked my mother--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--or my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only-- only haphazardly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was taking-- I was getting Hebrew lessons from my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- that's-- that's when we started getting cut off--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from old friends and family, when we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, we had a huge family that had lived in Poland for hundreds and hundreds of years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto, there were my grandparents, two of my aunts, my parents, and I, and a few other relatives.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it didn't have walls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put up some kind of a-- a-- fences.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it didn't have walls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was very dangerous to venture outside, which some people did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You were-- you were either put in jail or shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It just happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I think of it as sort of-- I call it salami tactics, where they abrogate a little bit of your freedom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cut off one piece of salami, and then another piece of salami.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the time you get through, there's nothing left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you're practically used to-- to the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only from hearsay.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't-- I-- I didn't personally see any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that we were very crowded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents were complaining about not being able to get enough food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were fairly wealthy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in the ghetto, they still helped each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was subsequently where it was every-- every dog for himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we used to-- we used to, for instance-- we used to come together and drink coffee and schnapps, and occasionally cake.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would sing all kinds of songs, most of them anti-German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We thought we were real revolutionaries.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
